testingmongo
Class TestMongoLocally

java.lang.Object
  testingmongo.TestMongoLocally

public class TestMongoLocally
extends java.lang.Object

This test is only runnable if you have a local mongo db started locally with standard configuration this mongo db must be populated with appsgate property entries. This test class IS NOT designed for extensive unit tests, the purpose is to play with the DB and provides some examples.

thibaud
